    • メソッドの詳細

      • toTagValue

        public static java.lang.Object toTagValue(Tag<?> t)
        Takes in an NBT tag, sanely checks null status, and then returns its value.
        パラメータ:
        t - Tag to get value from
        戻り値:
        tag value as an object or null if no value

      • getTagValue

        public static <T> T getTagValue(Tag<?> t,
                                java.lang.Class<? extends T> clazz)
        Takes in an NBT tag, sanely checks null status, and then returns it value. This method will return null if the value cannot be cast to the given class.
        パラメータ:
        t - Tag to get the value from
        clazz - the return type to use
        戻り値:
        the value as an onbject of the same type as the given class

      • toTagValue

        public static <T,U extends T> T toTagValue(Tag<?> t,
                                           java.lang.Class<? extends T> clazz,
                                           U defaultValue)
        Takes in an NBT tag, sanely checks null status, and then returns it value. This method will return null if the value cannot be cast to the default value.
        パラメータ:
        t - Tag to get the value from
        defaultValue - the value to return if the tag or its value is null or the value cannot be cast
        戻り値:
        the value as an onbject of the same type as the default value, or the default value
